Package hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen

Class LitmusX86BaseListener

java.lang.Object
hu.bme.mit.theta.litmus2xcfa.dsl.gen.LitmusX86BaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
LitmusX86Listener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public class LitmusX86BaseListener extends Object implements LitmusX86Listener
This class provides an empty implementation of LitmusX86Listener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
